## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the subjective nature of opinions on prisoners' rights. The sources used provide a snapshot of current debates but may not encompass all perspectives or recent legal developments. Additionally, the complexity of legal frameworks across different jurisdictions can lead to variations in the application and interpretation of prisoners' rights.